[Cite as 5/15/2002 Case Announcements, 2002-0hio-2230.]

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

May 15, 2002

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2002-0514. State ex rel. Belcastro v. Court of Appeals, Eighth Appellate Dist.

In Procedendo. On motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer and Cook, JJ., concur. Moyer, C.J., and Lundberg Stratton, J., dissent and would grant an alternative writ.
